      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOT A MESSAGE (3) finished second (22.68) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 7th at Wagga. Has a good record here at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Should bounce back. BIG BIG BEAR (1) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 1.3 lengths second (25.78) behind Kraken Missiles at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to feature again. BELGIUM SLICE (6) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Bendigo over 425m behind Rev Treasure (24.49) in a Grade 5. The form out of her last race has been franked. Worth another chance. BLUES TRAIN (7) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
